cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.GR, cs.HC 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with sketch analysis tasks such as sketch recognition, synthesis, and fine-grained sketch-based image retrieval. 
2. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper proposes a model for abstract sketch generation through reinforcement learning. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper uses reinforcement learning for stroke removal policy learning. 
4. cs.GR (Graphics) is relevant as the paper deals with human free-hand sketches. 
5. cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is relevant as the paper discusses the challenge of dealing with drastically different human drawing styles.
